// If TDCG meet and at least one compound meets TDCG chemical limit

$L1Limit = $c2h2.aggregate(endValue(true), $coev, durationKey()) > 3 or $c2h4.aggregate(endValue(true), $coev, durationKey()) >75 or $c2h6.aggregate(endValue(true), $coev, durationKey()) > 75 or $c4m.aggregate(endValue(true), $coev, durationKey()) > 75 or $co.aggregate(endValue(true), $coev, durationKey()) > 700 or $h2.aggregate(endValue(true), $coev, durationKey()) > 100
// Compare monthly generation rate of each chemical to its G2 Limit

$G2Limit =  $c2h2.aggregate(rate('day'), $coev, durationKey()).convertUnits('/mo') > 3 or $h2.aggregate(rate('day'), $coev, durationKey()).convertUnits('/mo') > 50 or $c4m.aggregate(rate('day'), $coev, durationKey()).convertUnits('/mo') > 38 or $c2h4.aggregate(rate('day'), $coev, durationKey()).convertUnits('/mo') > 38 or $c2h6.aggregate(rate('day'), $coev, durationKey()).convertUnits('/mo') > 38 or $co.aggregate(rate('day'), $coev, durationKey()).convertUnits('/mo') > 350
